<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/103000903/2025-26/evaluation> a ns1:EvaluationSystem ;
    ns1:evaluationDescription """Continuous Evaluacion
Research work (Exam):
Individual research work about one of the topics presented in class
The students can choose a topic of interest for them.
50% of the grade of the subject.

Test Exam
Test about graph minning and/or analysis of social networks.
50% of the grade of the subject
Recovey exam
The student has a second chance to present one of the works (Research work or Practical work).

Extraordinary Exams.
Individual research work (50%)
Test Exam (50%)"""@es ;
